# Agent tooling/process docs - not secrets (no credentials live here, ever -
# that's Doppler-only), just kept off the public repo. Lives in the private
# companion repo recruitflow-ai-agents instead - run
# scripts/sync-agent-files.sh to pull it into place (needed once per clone
# and once per new worktree).
